lead_paragraph: Monaco overtook Nice at the top of Ligue 1 with a 1-1 draw at Dijon on Tuesday but were denied all three points when Frederic Sammaritano struck an 87th-minute equaliser for the home side.

headline.print_headline: Title Hopefuls Monaco Held After Late Dijon Strike
